rows.label: qst201312_msg0001
rows.name:
You're looking for the
missing kids too, are you?

rows.label: qst201312_msg0002
rows.name:
I only just found this out myself,
but someone heard they were going
to play around Lake Varna.

rows.label: qst201312_msg0003
rows.name:
That place is much too dangerous for
children, so I'm not sure I believe
it myself, but you never do know...

rows.label: qst201312_msg0004
rows.name:
I just wish I knew where they are
now. You don't think they're hurt,
do you? They must be so hungry...

rows.label: qst201312_msg0005
rows.name:
Oh, it drives me crazy
thinking about it!
